              "quote": "SEON is designed seeking for: (i) taking advantage of well-founded ontologies (all its ontologies are ultimately grounded in UFO); (ii) providing ontology reusability and productivity, supported by core ontologies organized as Ontology Pattern Languages; and (iii) solving ontology integration problems by providing integration mechanisms.",
